'''Cape Verdean Gabonese''' are [[Gabon]]ese residents whose ancestry originated in [[Cape Verde]].
In 1995, it was estimated that there were 3,000 people of Cape Verdean descent in the [[Gabon]].<ref>[http://www.umassd.edu/SpecialPrograms/CaboVerde/wwpopest.html 1995 Cape Verdean Diaspora Population Estimates] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829094133/http://www.umassd.edu/SpecialPrograms/CaboVerde/wwpopest.html |date=2009-08-29 }}</ref>
